# type: Brief description (max 72 chars)

# Valid types: feat, fix, test, docs, chore, refactor

# Body (optional, wrap at 72 chars):
# - What changed
# - Why it changed
# - Any breaking changes

# Examples:
# feat: add user authentication with JWT
# fix: prevent null pointer in user profile
# docs: update API documentation for auth endpoints
# test: add integration tests for login flow
# chore: update dependencies and gitignore
# refactor: extract helper functions from controller

# Commit message format (conventional commits):
# type: description
#
# Rules:
# - Use imperative mood ("add" not "added")
# - Lowercase description (unless proper noun)
# - No period at end
# - Keep under 72 characters
# - Describe WHAT changed, not your thoughts
